        Component(settingspanel, "SettingsPanel", "settings/SettingsPanel.tsx", "Settings section (ADR-0018 §5). Context window select (4K–1M, F14) + 60/20/5/15 budget split display; IT/EN language toggle (F16); read-only provider list; reset button (clears localStorage). Reads settingsStore + providerStore.")
